      <title>由于买家对行业感到不满，曾经受人喜爱的电动汽车初创公司摇摇欲坠</title>
      <link>https://www.bloomberg.com/news/articles/2024-05-08/once-loved-ev-startups-rivn-lcid-teeter-on-edge-as-buyers-sour-on-industry</link>
      <description><![CDATA[电动汽车需求放缓引发了残酷的价格战，就连行业巨头特斯拉公司也难以应对。但对于这场竞赛的新进入者来说，这很快就会变成一场生存之战。]]></description>
      <guid>https://www.bloomberg.com/news/articles/2024-05-08/once-loved-ev-startups-rivn-lcid-teeter-on-edge-as-buyers-sour-on-industry</guid>
