      <link>https://www.bloomberg.com/news/articles/2024-05-08/in-iceland-world-s-biggest-carbon-removal-plant-run-by-climeworks-comes-online</link>
      <description><![CDATA[Climeworks 的 Mammoth 工厂每年将从空气中吸收 36,000 吨二氧化碳，其目标是到本十年末达到 100 万吨。]]></description>
